---

<div class="pharma-morphine-vs-kratom"><div class="sheet-inner">

  <div class="mast">
    <div class="kicker">Pharmacological &amp; Structural Comparison &mdash; &micro;-Opioid Receptor Ligands</div>
    <h1 class="title">Morphine vs. <em>Mitragyna</em> Alkaloids: Structure, Modification &amp; &micro;-Opioid Receptor Binding</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A side-by-side look at morphine and six kratom-derived indole alkaloids &mdash; how small structural changes (hydroxylation, acetylation, double-bond reduction, oxidation) shift binding affinity and pharmacology at the &micro;-opioid receptor.</p>
  </div>

